Development
SDLC - Software Development Lifice Cycle
-----------------

GitHub CI/CD|1. Writing code
GitLab CI/CD|2. Commit into SC (Git)
Jenkins		|3. Testing
TeamCity	|4. Build
Azure ADOPS	|5. Deployment

DevOps - is a philosofy or set of practicess to automate developmnet process.


